This paper is primarily focused on video action recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which is a common theme in the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with video data, which is a topic covered in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of distillation, which is a technique commonly used in neural network compression (cs.NE).
